cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with a multimodal dataset consisting of text and images suitable for English-Hindi multimodal machine translation task and multimodal research. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves computer vision and image processing, which suggests the category cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning and deep learning techniques, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence and natural language processing, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves multimodal research, which suggests the category cs.MM (Multimedia).
